{"tid":717450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"LBJ轉會就玩直播,PG就拍連續劇","createTime":"2018-06-26T04:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T05:21:32.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07620f04569716c14aa0c73644a43d8dcd80133b","tid":717450,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:45:49.000Z","msg":"虎撲6月26日訊據雷霆記者Brett Dawson報導，雷霆前鋒保羅-喬治拍攝了一部名為《保羅-喬治：我的旅程》的連續劇，講述他這個休賽期的故事，並解析他即將做出的決定。<br />\n<br />\n這部連續劇將於當地時間週二下午5點首映，共分3集播放。<br />\n<br />\n第一集講述的是喬治成長為NBA球星的過程。<br />\n<br />\n第二集追踪了他的球場外的生活，以及他如何做好準備來打造自己的職業生涯，將於當地時間6月28日上映。<br />\n<br />\n第三集將在喬治公開自己的決定後上映，分析他接下來的道路，以及他是如何做出這一決定的。每集的時間大約為6分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n喬治需要在接下來幾天內決定是否執行他下賽季價值2070萬美元的球員選項。若跳出合同，他將成為完全自由球員，並在雷霆、湖人等追求者中做出選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係當自己球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c8018fe3cc8b2f107ebc3a65179b4442370186","tid":717450,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"c706ae7a65db1b093e5bc22e08f54ae64d913cde","tid":717450,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"6分鐘一集，一睇連續劇以為廿幾分鐘，<br />\n心諗有冇咁撚多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2b89b1d4119631de640f667b82d4bf402e6072","tid":717450,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"第一集<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C8xn253W0AAGvLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC8xn253W0AAGvLR.jpg&h=5ab5ffae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3553a3ff403b4c9935357e0fb599cbe42fe8b645","tid":717450,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q9KF-qJVmo0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq9KF-qJVm